     "group": "Wireless networks",
     "name": "overview",
     "prose": {
      "en": "# Introduction to wireless networks\n\nThis section describes the controls applicable to wireless networks and extends upon the ‘Network design and configuration’ section of these guidelines.\n\n# Further information\n\nFurther information on [Wi-Fi technologies and associated testing and certification programs](#a9b6660b-fc4c-4a08-8db6-1130370b6b09) is available from the Wi-Fi Alliance.\n\nFurther information on cyber supply chain risk management can be found in the ‘Cyber supply chain risk management’ section of the [Guidelines for procurement and outsourcing](#f37a4848-0791-4870-b316-5536c2681c28).\n\nFurther information on evaluated products can be found in the ‘Evaluated product procurement’ section of the [Guidelines for evaluated products](#a699a3aa-828d-479b-b50b-98127bb19437).\n\nFurther information on encrypting communications can be found in the ‘Cryptographic fundamentals’ section of the [Guidelines for cryptography](#195abe87-bb1e-4006-8b42-eaecca4d51f1)."
     }
